INTERSHOP IOM 5.0.0-SNAPSHOT Database Model   (revision 948e75add5e9293702cd9035d82907f790621cc8)

Table oms.CacheStateDO

List of internal caches, used mainly for configurable objects like shops and supliers. The caches should be cleared after any configuration change (see function oms.clear_cache_request).

Columns 

References[1] Column Type Constraints[2] Default Comment
id bigint PK, UNIQUE, NOT_NULL  
cacheName varchar(255) only the name "bakery-cache-config" is used for now. 
clearDate timestamp without time zone Timestamp of the last cache clear for the cache and the server. 
serverId varchar(255) NOT_NULL Unique identifier for a server. 
action text Specifies under which circumstances the cache was cleared. 

[1] Not all references are enforced by a foreign key where they could.
Such "missing" foreign keys are denoted with [[ ]].

[2] Constraints:
PK : the column is part of the primary key
UNIQUE: does don't cover unique constraints and indexes defined on more than one column.

Constraints and Indexes 

Type Name Definition
